        BiocGenerics, S4Vectors, lme4, methods, mgcv, pheatmap,
        purrr, rlang, grDevices, IRanges, stats
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
